{"TopicId":200473,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"MechJeb and RCS efficiency","CreatedByName":"chd","CreatedById":78680,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-19T01:00:36Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"chd","CreatedById":78680,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-19T01:00:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMostly just curious here -- when I use MechJeb\u0027s landing guidance with \u0022use \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E for small adjustments\u0022 checked, and also sometimes with the docking autopilot, it looks like it\u0027s firing a lot more of the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E thrusters than it actually would need to in order to translate in the desired direction. Sometimes it looks like it\u0027s firing essentially all of them, though not all at the same thrust. Sometimes it appears to cycle through them all, fairly rapidly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat\u0027s MechJeb doing here? I usually assume that it\u0027s going to be better at this stuff than I would be doing it by hand, but it\u0027s use of \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E often at least appears to be fairly inexplicable. Is MechJeb just bad at this, or do I not appreciate it enough? \u003Cspan\u003E:-)\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anonymous49","CreatedById":209341,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-19T04:57:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthat never happened to me\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-19T07:49:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn regards to \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E, mechjeb is far from efficient. It gets the job done, sure, but it\u0027s expensive job. That\u0027s why I learned to dock manually,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidSquid","CreatedById":196199,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-19T08:03:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI much prefer to dock manually, using the DPAI mod for visual aid. Way faster, more efficient, more safe.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jimmymcgoochie","CreatedById":199902,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-19T11:06:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u2019t let MechJeb use \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E unless absolutely necessary- in stock KSP reaction wheels alone should be enough to rotate your vessel in whatever direction is needed. It\u2019s probably firing most/all of your thrusters because the mass/thrust is imbalanced when it tries to fire translation controls, resulting in a rotation which requires correction by firing more thrusters, which messes up the translation and so on in a loop.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spricigo","CreatedById":166502,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-19T11:41:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223928599\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200473\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221613696436\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278680\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022chd\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, chd said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs MechJeb just bad at this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyes. ( \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/199902-jimmymcgoochie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022199902\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/199902-jimmymcgoochie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@jimmymcgoochie\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0nailed it: imbalance and overcorrection)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso don\u0027t help if you\u00A0didn\u0027t designed the craft to minimize the issue.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Curveball Anders","CreatedById":107529,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-19T15:08:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s has a problem with over powered \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo one way to make it work more efficient is to dial down the power of the trusters.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"chd","CreatedById":78680,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-19T23:03:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks all -- this makes sense. It\u0027s too bad there isn\u0027t a hybrid setting, \u0022use \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E for translation only, use reaction wheels for rotation.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidSquid","CreatedById":196199,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-19T23:09:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTry out the DPAI mod\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002277044\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed616943083\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/40423-181-docking-port-alignment-indicator-version-685-updated-121419/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:195px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nand you\u0027ll be amazed how fast and easy you can do docking.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spricigo","CreatedById":166502,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-20T03:03:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223929178\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200473\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221613775835\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278680\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022chd\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, chd said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks all -- this makes sense. It\u0027s too bad there isn\u0027t a hybrid setting, \u0022use \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E for translation only, use reaction wheels for rotation.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can set the thrusters to only respond to translation inputs:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nEnable Advanced Tweakables\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nOpen the Part Action Window\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nClick Show Activation Toggles\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nTurn off\u00A0 Yaw, Pitch and Roll\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidSquid","CreatedById":196199,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-20T03:12:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis can be automated by this community \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Module Manager (mod)\u0022\u003EMM\u003C/abbr\u003E patch written by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/125662-snark/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022125662\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/125662-snark/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Snark\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003E// Configure \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E to Translate Only by Default\u003Cbr\u003E\n// Author: Snark\u003Cbr\u003E\n@PART[*]:HAS[@MODULE[ModuleRCSFX]]\u003Cbr\u003E\n{\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0@MODULE[ModuleRCSFX]\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0{\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0%enableYaw = false\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0%enablePitch = false\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0%enableRoll = false\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0}\u003Cbr\u003E\n}\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022110959\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1649284972\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/139980-130-community-database-of-module-manager-patches-for-stock-ksp/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:195px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"antipro","CreatedById":173370,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-20T08:03:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223929178\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200473\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221613775835\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278680\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022chd\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, chd said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s too bad there isn\u0027t a hybrid setting, \u0022use \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E for translation only, use reaction wheels for rotation.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nactually, there\u0027s a setting about that:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Mechjeb (mod)\u0022\u003EMJ\u003C/abbr\u003E - SmartRCS - uncheck \u0022use \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E for Rotation\u0022\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}